      - status: stable
        content:
          name: BusinessCenters
          description: |
            A class for specifying the business day calendar location used in determining whether a day is a business day or not, either by specifying this business center by reference to an enumerated list that is maintained by the FpML standard, or by reference to such specification when it exists elsewhere as part of the instance document. This class corresponds to the FpML BusinessCentersOrReference.model.
          namespace:
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
            value: cdm/base/datetime
          businessCenter:
            description: |
              A code identifying one or several business day calendar location(s). The set of business day calendar locations are specified by the business day calendar location enumeration which is maintained by the FpML standard.
            type:
              blueId: 6aehfNAxHLC1PHHoDr3tYtFH3RWNbiWdFancJ1bypXEY
            itemType:
              blueId: oTpGdJoCGs6bye7euLM5RaGh8sDGwEjdHJVFgCxiC6T
            schema:
              minItems:
                type:
                  blueId: 5WNMiV9Knz63B4dVY5JtMyh3FB4FSGqv7ceScvuapdE1
                value: 0
          businessCentersReference:
            description: A reference to a financial business center location specified elsewhere in the instance document.
            type:
              blueId: Gxef9Ao3kTD6W3FqiEvpaQ3PXH9nMAzm4B5vGBzJ41ZU
          commodityBusinessCalendar:
            type:
              blueId: 6aehfNAxHLC1PHHoDr3tYtFH3RWNbiWdFancJ1bypXEY
            itemType:
              blueId: HwvjSsLi4YiJyxebuw3fRGRgwmLSPLhtuYwahUNMGuRr
            schema:
              minItems:
                type:
                  blueId: 5WNMiV9Knz63B4dVY5JtMyh3FB4FSGqv7ceScvuapdE1
                value: 0
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 3
            typeBlueId: HujWuka613tVBGR9SknuY73FEbD163xzBbEmUfRCTtF9
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: BusinessCenterTime
          description: A class for defining a time with respect to a business day calendar location. For example, 11:00:00 GBLO.
          namespace:
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
            value: cdm/base/datetime
          businessCenter:
            description: |
              A code identifying a business day calendar location. A business day calendar location is drawn from the list identified by the business day calendar location enumeration.
            type:
              blueId: oTpGdJoCGs6bye7euLM5RaGh8sDGwEjdHJVFgCxiC6T
            schema:
              required:
                type:
                  blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
                value: true
          hourMinuteTime:
            description: |
              A time specified in hh:mm:ss format where the second component must be '00', e.g. 11am would be represented as 11:00:00.
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
            schema:
              required:
                type:
                  blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
                value: true
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 3
            typeBlueId: ETs9sz3NN8RvLtTf1kAJnYcSLRTW91uqxzhL5q7jTEuK
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: BusinessDateRange
          description: |
            A class defining a range of contiguous business days by defining an unadjusted first date, an unadjusted last date and a business day convention and business centers for adjusting the first and last dates if they would otherwise fall on a non business day in the specified business centers. The days between the first and last date must also be good business days in the specified centers to be counted in the range.
          namespace:
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
            value: cdm/base/datetime
          businessCenters:
            description: |
              The business center(s), specified either explicitly or by reference to those specified somewhere else in the instance document.
            type:
              blueId: HujWuka613tVBGR9SknuY73FEbD163xzBbEmUfRCTtF9
          businessDayConvention:
            description: |
              The convention for adjusting a date if it would otherwise fall on a day that is not a business day, as specified by an ISDA convention (e.g. Following, Precedent).
            type:
              blueId: FYjKvmcTzRNBddpxNjEdu31EQrd26VAAYESVaWq8SfR4
            schema:
              required:
                type:
                  blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
                value: true
          endDate:
            description: The last date of a date range.
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
          startDate:
            description: The first date of a date range.
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 3
            typeBlueId: HwkXPt7HALSThM7DRZPLAehRt24HBL3oCWd71G2XWvmc
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: BusinessDayAdjustments
          description: |
            A class defining the business day convention and financial business centers used for adjusting any relevant date if it would otherwise fall on a day that is not a business day in the specified business center.
          namespace:
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
            value: cdm/base/datetime
          businessCenters:
            description: |
              The business center(s), specified either explicitly or by reference to those specified somewhere else in the instance document.
            type:
              blueId: HujWuka613tVBGR9SknuY73FEbD163xzBbEmUfRCTtF9
          businessDayConvention:
            description: The convention for adjusting a date if it would otherwise fall on a day that is not a business day.
            type:
              blueId: FYjKvmcTzRNBddpxNjEdu31EQrd26VAAYESVaWq8SfR4
            schema:
              required:
                type:
                  blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
                value: true
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 3
            typeBlueId: G6NRh7uJ9nHqamG4NyjfGcr5Wfk3qujsowe9hwpvpBNp
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: BusinessDayConventionEnum
          description: |
            The enumerated values to specify the convention for adjusting any relevant date if it would otherwise fall on a day that is not a valid business day.
          type:
            blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
          namespace:
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
            value: cdm/base/datetime
          schema:
            enum:
              items:
                - type:
                    blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
                  value: FOLLOWING
                - type:
                    blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
                  value: FRN
                - type:
                    blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
                  value: MODFOLLOWING
                - type:
                    blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
                  value: MODPRECEDING
                - type:
                    blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
                  value: NEAREST
                - type:
                    blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
                  value: NONE
                - type:
                    blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
                  value: NotApplicable
                - type:
                    blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
                  value: PRECEDING
