      - status: stable
        content:
          name: CalculationMethodEnum
          description: |
            What calculation type is required, averaging or compounding. This enumeration is used to represent the definitions of modular calculated rates as described in the 2021 ISDA Definitions, section 7.
          type:
            blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
          namespace:
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
            value: cdm/observable/asset/calculatedrate
          schema:
            enum:
              items:
                - type:
                    blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
                  value: Averaging
                - type:
                    blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
                  value: CompoundedIndex
                - type:
                    blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
                  value: Compounding
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 3
            typeBlueId: F6zrf4BEXM9uC8huzSYoDyjeui85qhLouK5shmCrqPbq
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: CalculationPeriod
          description: |
            A data defining:  the parameters used in the calculation of a fixed or floating rate calculation period amount. This data forms:  part of cashflows representation of a swap stream.
          namespace:
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
            value: cdm/product/common/schedule
          adjustedEndDate:
            description: The calculation period end date, adjusted according to any relevant business day convention.
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
          adjustedStartDate:
            description: The calculation period start date, adjusted according to any relevant business day convention.
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
          calculationPeriodNumberOfDays:
            description: |
              The number of days from the adjusted effective / start date to the adjusted termination / end date calculated in accordance with the applicable day count fraction.
            type:
              blueId: 5WNMiV9Knz63B4dVY5JtMyh3FB4FSGqv7ceScvuapdE1
          dayCountYearFraction:
            description: |
              The year fraction value of the calculation period, result of applying the ISDA rules for day count fraction defined in the ISDA Annex.
            type:
              blueId: 7pwXmXYCJtWnd348c2JQGBkm9C4renmZRwxbfaypsx5y
          fixedRate:
            description: |
              The calculation period fixed rate. A per annum rate, expressed as a decimal. A fixed rate of 5% would be represented as 0.05.
            type:
              blueId: 7pwXmXYCJtWnd348c2JQGBkm9C4renmZRwxbfaypsx5y
          floatingRateDefinition:
            description: The floating rate reset information for the calculation period.
            type:
              blueId: 96cxSQ6LVE5Lwx3Z16xFUstP1FT1SpP6841CUzJHZGWq
          forecastAmount:
            description: |
              The amount representing the forecast of the accrued value of the calculation period. An intermediate value used to generate the forecastPaymentAmount in the PaymentCalculationPeriod.
            type:
              blueId: AbAR9hDgkuDPyGUVbpg2virbQmHfou9H5TMSUKaAAQo3
          forecastRate:
            description: |
              A value representing the forecast rate used to calculate the forecast future value of the accrual period. This is a calculated rate determined based on averaging the rates in the rateObservation elements, and incorporates all of the rate treatment and averaging rules. A value of 1% should be represented as 0.01.
            type:
              blueId: 7pwXmXYCJtWnd348c2JQGBkm9C4renmZRwxbfaypsx5y
          fxLinkedNotionalAmount:
            description: |
              The amount that a cashflow will accrue interest on. This is the calculated amount of the FX linked - i.e. the other currency notional amount multiplied by the appropriate FX spot rate.
            type:
              blueId: 3yieueonTuUbuRSGGjTXbPYRXwfv92VC2gsTyzD9Sh1x
          notionalAmount:
            description: The amount that a cashflow will accrue interest on.
            type:
              blueId: 7pwXmXYCJtWnd348c2JQGBkm9C4renmZRwxbfaypsx5y
          unadjustedEndDate:
            description: The calculation end date, unadjusted.
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
          unadjustedStartDate:
            description: The calculation start date, unadjusted.
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 3
            typeBlueId: 6WejDtDyb49aopgshCUtasaaJZDLogshESyrCgFc2kCz
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
