      - status: stable
        content:
          name: Cash
          description: |
            An Asset that consists solely of a monetary holding in a currency. The currency of the Cash asset is held in the string Identifier (from AssetBase) and the AssetIdTypeEnum must be set to define that a CurrencyCode is set.  The function SetCashCurrency can be used to create (or update) a Cash object and the function GetCashCurrency can be used to retrieve the currency of a Cash object.
          namespace:
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
            value: cdm/base/staticdata/asset/common
          exchange:
            description: If the Asset is listed, defines the public exchange of the listing.
            type:
              blueId: 9q5Aqc2sXyQHBEB1fEH7YnXg3xyueB94fHUPswAoFjxZ
          identifier:
            description: Asset Identifiers are used to uniquely identify an Asset, using a specified Asset Identifier Type.
            type:
              blueId: 6aehfNAxHLC1PHHoDr3tYtFH3RWNbiWdFancJ1bypXEY
            itemType:
              blueId: 2aVbLJJSBqA4CEk4y99kfeaGjWR1LMijC7oGiybxWqC4
            schema:
              minItems:
                type:
                  blueId: 5WNMiV9Knz63B4dVY5JtMyh3FB4FSGqv7ceScvuapdE1
                value: 1
          isExchangeListed:
            description: Defines whether the Asset is listed on a public exchange.
            type:
              blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
          relatedExchange:
            description: Provides the related Exchanges, if applicable.
            type:
              blueId: 6aehfNAxHLC1PHHoDr3tYtFH3RWNbiWdFancJ1bypXEY
            itemType:
              blueId: 9q5Aqc2sXyQHBEB1fEH7YnXg3xyueB94fHUPswAoFjxZ
            schema:
              minItems:
                type:
                  blueId: 5WNMiV9Knz63B4dVY5JtMyh3FB4FSGqv7ceScvuapdE1
                value: 0
          taxonomy:
            description: |
              Defines the taxonomy of an object by combining a taxonomy source (i.e. the rules to classify the object) and a value (i.e. the output of those rules on the object.
            type:
              blueId: 6aehfNAxHLC1PHHoDr3tYtFH3RWNbiWdFancJ1bypXEY
            itemType:
              blueId: HFNW44RszHHmv3rZU8MyQULFubFmMwmZvmNHgpUek4vb
            schema:
              minItems:
                type:
                  blueId: 5WNMiV9Knz63B4dVY5JtMyh3FB4FSGqv7ceScvuapdE1
                value: 0
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 3
            typeBlueId: BXfHe5xVoB8FixQGaJjUB9VefbfmoE6eatZzYkKysf2b
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: CashCollateralValuationMethod
          description: |
            This type is a generic structure that can represent the parameters of several mid-market valuation and replacement value methods described in the 2021 ISDA Definitions.
          namespace:
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
            value: cdm/observable/asset
          agreedDiscountRate:
            description: This may be used to indicate the discount rate to be used for cash collateral for cash settlement purposes.
            type:
              blueId: DkAAYuMhrcUQRrFdCEPKwcQDCnee3rxTu6vYVSURpWWY
          applicableCsa:
            description: |
              This may be used to specify what type of CSA (credit support annex/agreement) is to be used for cash settlement purposes.
            type:
              blueId: 75c1yTeep3izcexCwE39ggRt7NHoUHLkxKh5UBnGhWAC
          cashCollateralCurrency:
            description: This may be used to indicate the currency of cash collateral for cash settlement purposes.
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
          cashCollateralInterestRate:
            description: This may be used to indicate the interest rate to be used for cash collateral for cash settlement purposes.
            type:
              blueId: DkAAYuMhrcUQRrFdCEPKwcQDCnee3rxTu6vYVSURpWWY
          prescribedDocumentationAdjustment:
            description: This may be used to indicate that 'prescribed documentation adjustment' is applicable.
            type:
              blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
          protectedParty:
            description: This may be used to specify which party is protected (e.g. under Replacement Value cash settlement methods).
            type:
              blueId: 6aehfNAxHLC1PHHoDr3tYtFH3RWNbiWdFancJ1bypXEY
            itemType:
              blueId: AAT6S15uy3hYt9iAvjeNRh4qvGHZEmvVYW2zF5yVmhqr
            schema:
              minItems:
                type:
                  blueId: 5WNMiV9Knz63B4dVY5JtMyh3FB4FSGqv7ceScvuapdE1
                value: 0
              maxItems:
                type:
                  blueId: 5WNMiV9Knz63B4dVY5JtMyh3FB4FSGqv7ceScvuapdE1
                value: 2
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 3
            typeBlueId: BEKWCv1WpmaFsqVkWUWnM3WB5WJpUUGuUm1vDnJcgTHj
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: Cashflow
          description: |
            Class to specify a cashflow, i.e. the outcome of either of computation (e.g. interest accrual) or an assessment of some sort (e.g. a fee). The cashflow can then be turned into a cash transfer, artefact to be used as the input to a payment system or the outcome of it. The associated globalKey denotes the ability to associate a hash value to the Cashflow instantiations for the purpose of model cross-referencing, in support of functionality such as the event effect and the lineage.
          namespace:
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
            value: cdm/product/common/settlement
          asset:
            description: Represents the object that is subject to the transfer, it could be an asset or a reference.
            type:
              blueId: Ha46gf3kVKXBNGggEB3oSexk9WX18MmmWrLadADimzeB
          cashflowType:
            description: |
              The qualification of the type of cashflow, e.g. brokerage fee, premium, upfront fee etc. Particularly relevant when it cannot be inferred directly through lineage.
            type:
              blueId: HFLE8QVSxkYmjLKtwEnzRTkupVu8kcpZnikU9B8bnSH3
            schema:
              required:
                type:
                  blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
                value: true
          payerReceiver:
            description: Specifies who pays / receives the cashflow, though a normalised Party1 / Party2 enumerator.
            type:
              blueId: CNBnVnWSC7atVmZFrAE1NPVmcdah8bgGoEUdZ9fxKq75
            schema:
              required:
                type:
                  blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
                value: true
          paymentDiscounting:
            description: |
              FpML specifies the FpML PaymentDiscounting.model group for representing the discounting elements that can be associated with a payment.
            type:
              blueId: 3vicc7as3nn2YJ2rjji6rMd8bpBRgzRM3q4GYempHppN
          quantity:
            description: |
              Represents the amount of the asset to be transferred. The cashflow amount is always a positive number, as the cashflow direction is implied by the payer/receiver attribute.
            type:
              blueId: LzqjcnUmDthjDZkgp95CFhWjxPvLYNv2nrFan3MHY99
          settlementDate:
            description: Represents the date on which the transfer to due.
            type:
              blueId: FYJyVGYxP2GD7vW6m7fwvfBppdWaSDvxizuhuvvgtibD
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 3
            typeBlueId: 4ZiCrYCYd4S7KUQNZk1v2d6TA68XChy7R8cbY4LZBGVw
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: CashflowRepresentation
          description: |
            A data defining:  the cashflow representation of a swap trade.
          namespace:
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
            value: cdm/product/asset
          cashflowsMatchParameters:
            description: |
              A true/false flag to indicate whether the cashflows match the parametric definition of the stream, i.e. whether the cashflows could be regenerated from the parameters without loss of information.
            type:
              blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
            schema:
              required:
                type:
                  blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
                value: true
          paymentCalculationPeriod:
            description: |
              The adjusted payment date and associated calculation period parameters required to calculate the actual or projected payment amount. A list of payment calculation period elements may be ordered in the document by ascending adjusted payment date. An FpML document containing an unordered list of payment calculation periods is still regarded as a conformant document.
            type:
              blueId: 6aehfNAxHLC1PHHoDr3tYtFH3RWNbiWdFancJ1bypXEY
            itemType:
              blueId: 9jwptYwf7iHDmM6mNJvPxnXaFWTFGrDAiR4ii5JXuPbE
            schema:
              minItems:
                type:
                  blueId: 5WNMiV9Knz63B4dVY5JtMyh3FB4FSGqv7ceScvuapdE1
                value: 0
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 3
            typeBlueId: 296zD6PqeG38Q2xqEx71iYKy4cxQzbwkLgEiqE2FNY6h
            attributesAdded: []
