              Indicates if the collateral balance amount is based on pre or post haircut, if a haircut is associated with the collateral asset
            type:
              blueId: FmMeLshtR2TiGNydbXVUYvb5cgzKLqgxmnjV3MpLiXwh
          payerReceiver:
            description: |
              Specifies each of the parties in the collateral balance and its perspective with regards to the direction of the collateral balance, posted or received.
            type:
              blueId: DzcSyuRzPL3vpodnqxgMhmMGKDzwiLPEL3Gtk8rtVzr1
            schema:
              required:
                type:
                  blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
                value: true
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 3
            typeBlueId: 4tU5cfKeZno5jB7UN5smWaAt85EutMjDqZuWCsFcxUmX
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: CollateralCriteria
          description: |
            The possible different terms that can be combined, using AND, OR and NOT logic, to define the issuers and/or assets that meet a given criteria for collateral.
          namespace:
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
            value: cdm/product/collateral
          AllCriteria:
            description: Enables two or more Collateral Criteria to be combined using AND logic.
            type:
              blueId: this#3
          AnyCriteria:
            description: Enables two or more Collateral Criteria to be combined using OR logic.
            type:
              blueId: this#0
          AssetAgencyRating:
            description: Criteria is the agency rating(s) of the collateral asset.
            type:
              blueId: EDXdL3DpFgyCKf4MCKrXEq4dqsDKfyuPLZgnJrezHkPZ
          AssetCountryOfOrigin:
            description: Criteria is the collateral asset country of origin.
            type:
              blueId: 2F73RtgmE2N99HG6VQw7BNrtWcf4sQjQJ6zJ3Hp24XmS
          AssetMaturity:
            description: Criteria is the maturity characteristics of the collateral asset.
            type:
              blueId: 9UdmkhkDcVbAW2iVtkzN5GPHav1vvJaKeJVemKZVJDd5
          AssetType:
            description: Criteria is the asset type of the collateral.
            type:
              blueId: FRqYRTWRxZfg1RuMuPbNaxZkgGMc8oTTuf4gi5Mhrb8C
          CollateralIssuerType:
            description: Criteria is the type of entity issuing the asset.
            type:
              blueId: CUSCzsVUYy2xHJZtmwG5CREevRxEgURVHDk7QJm9UBmM
          CollateralTaxonomy:
            description: Criteria is the taxonomy characteristics of an collateral.
            type:
              blueId: D8uP5LJXUFTKyAG3mfHD1szhNTs8Gq8mFJbrrFvbiFdF
          CounterpartyOwnIssuePermitted:
            description: Criteria includes collateral issued by the counterparty.
            type:
              blueId: GdQdHRzaV1nDruUPUKDZcDZPnB1HTB2zX2FM1iVWaqJM
          CurrencyCodeEnum:
            description: Criteria is the denominated currency of the collateral.
            type:
