      - status: stable
        content:
          name: VarianceCapFloor
          namespace:
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
            value: cdm/product/asset
          boundedVariance:
            description: |
              Conditions which bound variance. The contract specifies one or more boundary levels. These levels are expressed as prices for confirmation purposes Underlyer price must be equal to or higher than Lower Barrier is known as Up Conditional Swap Underlyer price must be equal to or lower than Upper Barrier is known as Down Conditional Swap Underlyer price must be equal to or higher than Lower Barrier and must be equal to or lower than Upper Barrier is known as Barrier Conditional Swap.
            type:
              blueId: FTXPtBhhn7XSJ6iufLkKyZmKMQepYjYXUjdiP5KVjKki
          unadjustedVarianceCap:
            description: |
              For use when varianceCap is applicable. Contains the scaling factor of the Variance Cap that can differ on a trade-by-trade basis in the European market. For example, a Variance Cap of 2.5^2 x Variance Strike Price has an unadjustedVarianceCap of 2.5.
            type:
              blueId: 7pwXmXYCJtWnd348c2JQGBkm9C4renmZRwxbfaypsx5y
          varianceCap:
            description: If present and true, then variance cap is applicable.
            type:
              blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
            schema:
              required:
                type:
                  blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
                value: true
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 3
            typeBlueId: DMLhKawC3QT35JxvHmTtehjQ1swjtafRgKFoKSkneSTn
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: VarianceReturnTerms
          namespace:
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
            value: cdm/product/asset
          annualizationFactor:
            description: |
              This specifies the numerator of an annualization factor. Frequently this number is equal to the number of observations of prices in a year e.g. 252.
            type:
              blueId: 5WNMiV9Knz63B4dVY5JtMyh3FB4FSGqv7ceScvuapdE1
          dividendApplicability:
            description: The parameters which define whether dividends are applicable
            type:
              blueId: 7YPXekUAnhSyp9AcFCEqPbCAU21zbcDE5gTMTqxEu6f4
          equityUnderlierProvisions:
            description: Contains Equity Underlyer provisions regarding jurisdiction and fallbacks.
            type:
              blueId: 68bTDtRvgynPZurH7nT19Jy72N8v8n4ZcDksksPDZ3pd
          exchangeTradedContractNearest:
            description: Specification of the exchange traded contract nearest.
            type:
              blueId: FHPQdUTihAD2MKTuwZT6gCYYJ4M13BXwbsxais39tP97
          expectedN:
            description: Expected number of trading days.
            type:
              blueId: 5WNMiV9Knz63B4dVY5JtMyh3FB4FSGqv7ceScvuapdE1
          initialLevel:
            description: |
              Contract will strike off this initial level. Providing just the initialLevel without initialLevelSource, infers that this is AgreedInitialPrice - a specified Initial Index Level.
            type:
              blueId: 7pwXmXYCJtWnd348c2JQGBkm9C4renmZRwxbfaypsx5y
          initialLevelSource:
            description: In this context, this is AgreedInitialPrice - a specified Initial Index Level.
            type:
              blueId: A4xQ1M4K4Bxgfj42oJzfRc6Jc8n5qjBuZW3DA5zJEgMy
          meanAdjustment:
            description: |
              Specifies whether Mean Adjustment is applicable or not in the calculation of the Realized Volatility, Variance or Correlation
            type:
              blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
          performance:
            description: |
              Performance calculation, in accordance with Part 1 Section 12 of the 2018 ISDA CDM Equity Confirmation for Security Equity Swap, Para 75. 'Equity Performance'. Cumulative performance is used as a notional multiplier factor on both legs of an Equity Swap.
            type:
              blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
          sharePriceDividendAdjustment:
            description: Indicates whether the price of shares is adjusted for dividends or not.
            type:
              blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
          valuationTerms:
            description: Contains all non-date valuation information.
            type:
              blueId: HBPyekApP6oSxJLXSqMqQEf4uuZaocEC84epkGmriddV
          varianceCapFloor:
            description: Contains possible barriers for variance products, both variance-based and underlier price based
            type:
              blueId: DMLhKawC3QT35JxvHmTtehjQ1swjtafRgKFoKSkneSTn
          varianceStrikePrice:
            description: Variance Strike Price in accordance with the ISDA 2011 Equity Derivatives Definitions.
            type:
              blueId: 34JSSaiNLZkZGJCPhZGY4wsFrAd7HeP7M2MEwHXHZp2u
          vegaNotionalAmount:
            description: |
              Vega Notional represents the approximate gain/loss at maturity for a 1% difference between RVol (realised vol) and KVol (strike vol). It does not necessarily represent the Vega Risk of the trade.
            type:
              blueId: AryjbeXRD3NJGePy1YkXGQfEBmBk9CXhQ9DueVyyy3P
          volatilityCapFloor:
            description: Contains containing volatility-based barriers
            type:
              blueId: Ad6xt3gxZGZhgoVLeMQ7CEg6aLkmfkexpd4EFmE4kLzn
          volatilityStrikePrice:
            description: Volatility Strike Price in accordance with the ISDA 2011 Equity Derivatives Definitions.
            type:
              blueId: 34JSSaiNLZkZGJCPhZGY4wsFrAd7HeP7M2MEwHXHZp2u
